ypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2763620355/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2763620355","tinyui":"/x/A4C5p","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2763620355","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2763620355/Tentative+Initiatives","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2763620355"}},{"id":"2685632556","type":"page","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:page/2685632556","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmNvbnRlbnQvMjY4NTYzMjU1Ng==","status":"current","title":"SPI (Proyecto Iniciadores de Pago)","macroRenderedOutput":{},"extensions":{"position":376300866},"_expandable":{"container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","metadata":"","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2685632556/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2685632556/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2685632556/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2685632556/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2685632556","tinyui":"/x/LIATo","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2685632556","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2685632556/SPI+Proyecto+Iniciadores+de+Pago","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2685632556"}},{"id":"2593554528","type":"page","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:page/2593554528","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmNvbnRlbnQvMjU5MzU1NDUyOA==","status":"current","title":"SPI Estimation","macroRenderedOutput":{},"extensions":{"position":1406},"_expandable":{"container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","metadata":"","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2593554528/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2593554528/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2593554528/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2593554528/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2593554528","tinyui":"/x/YICWmg","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2593554528","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2593554528/SPI+Estimation","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2593554528"}}],"macroRenderedOutput":{},"body":{"storage":{"value":"<p>Confluence: <a href=\"https://jira.bancardnet.dom/confluence/pages/viewpage.action?spaceKey=PRYINPA&amp;title=Portal+de+comercios\">https://jira.bancardnet.dom/confluence/pages/viewpage.action?spaceKey=PRYINPA&amp;title=Portal+de+comercios</a></p><p /><h1>Introducci&oacute;n</h1><p>Esta iniciativa trata de incluir nueva informaci&oacute;n (provenientes del BUS) en las tablas raw_transactions y transactions para luego mostrarlas en los reportes de Ventas. Para ello es necesario crear un nuevo modelo asociado a las raw_transactions y transactions, y realizar todas las modificaciones en los endpoints y reportes para incluir un nuevo campo (en formato json).<br /></p><h1>Estimaci&oacute;n<br /></h1><table data-layout=\"default\" ac:local-id=\"1e3ea8da-0baa-4e75-8346-e829216caaaf\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 163.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 449.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 147.0px;\" /></colgroup><tbody><tr><th><p><strong>Proyecto</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Descripci&oacute;n</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Estimaci&oacute;n (hrs)</strong></p></th></tr><tr><td><p>commerce-service</p></td><td><p>Nuevo modelo para almacenar los datos adicionales de la transacci&oacute;n que viene del bus. <br />Contendr&aacute;: id, raw_transaction_id, transaction_id, customer_fields, billing_identifier, other_data (json)<br /></p><ac:image ac:align=\"center\" ac:layout=\"center\" ac:original-height=\"299\" ac:original-width=\"690\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"image-20230517-135116.png\" ri:version-at-save=\"1\" /></ac:image></td><td><p>8</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>commerce-service</p></td><td><p>Al momento de crear una raw_transaction, crear un registro en la nueva tabla (transaction_id en null)</p></td><td><p>12</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>commerce-service</p></td><td><p>Al momento de crear la transaction, buscar el registro en la nueva tabla (por raw_transaction_id) y actualizar el valor de transaction_id</p></td><td><p>12</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>commerce-service</p></td><td><p>Modificar el proceso de purga de transacciones, para purgar tambi&eacute;n registros de este nueva tabla (por transaction_id)</p></td><td><p>12</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>commerce-service</p></td><td><p>Agregar el campo transaction_additional_data en la respuesta del endpoint de movimientos de Ventas. Modificar dataset.</p></td><td><p>24</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>commerce-service</p></td><td><p>Modificar endpoint de descarga de csv (Ventas) para agregar el transaction_addictional_data. <br />Importante: solo para reporte &ldquo;con comisiones&rdquo; (que es cuando el usuario presiona el check en el portal de comercios).</p></td><td><p>20</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>commerce-suite</p></td><td><p>En la pantalla de Ventas, incluir los datos adicionales en cada transacci&oacute;n en la columna &ldquo;Usuario&rdquo;. <br />Si bien los datos adicionales los tomamos del campo &ldquo;other data&rdquo;, es un json. Analizar con Luis luego c&oacute;mo mostramos esos key/values dentro de la columna Usuario.</p></td><td><p>30</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>gesti&oacute;n</p></td><td><p>Gesti&oacute;n de Jira, Sprints, reuniones de seguimiento</p></td><td><p>15</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Total</p></td><td><p /></td><td><p>133</p></td></tr></tbody></table>","representation":"storage","embeddedContent":[],"_expandable":{"content":"/rest/api/content/2602991617"}},"_expandable":{"editor":"","atlas_doc_format":"","view":"","export_view":"","styled_view":"","dynamic":"","editor2":"","anonymous_export_view":""}},"extensions":{"position":824},"_expandable":{"childTypes":"","container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","schedulePublishInfo":"","metadata":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2602991617/child","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2602991617/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2602991617/history","draftVersion":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2602991617/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN"},"_links":{"editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2602991617","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2602991617/SPI+Iniciadores+de+Pagos+-+Portal+de+Comercios+-+Estimaci+n","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2602991617","context":"/wiki","self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2602991617","tinyui":"/x/AYAmmw","collection":"/rest/api/content","base":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki"}}